<div class="responsive-table">

    <h2>卖出富时100：详细示例</h2>

<table class="table-zebra-rows" border="1">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</td>
			<td style="text-align: center;"><strong>差价合约 现货</strong></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>基础市场/价值</strong></td>
